text: Jhulelal (Sindhi:جهوللال), Kutchi: ઝૂલેલાલ) is the Ishta Dev (community God) of Sindhi people. His birthday Cheti Chand falls on the second day of the Chaitra month. It is auspicious for Sindhis and celebrated all over the world. ==Notes== Category:Hindu gods and goddesses
title: Jhulelal (Hinduism)
